Class DbxUploadStyleBuilder<R,E,X extends Throwable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dropbox.core.v2.DbxUploadStyleBuilder<R,E,X>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - The return type of the DbxUploader
    E - The error type of the DbxUploader
    X - The exception type of the DbxUploader
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DbxFiles.UploadBuilder, DbxFiles.UploadSessionAppendBuilder, DbxFiles.UploadSessionFinishBuilder

    public abstract class DbxUploadStyleBuilder<R,E,X extends Throwable>
extends Object
    The common interface for all builders associated with download style methods. Use the start() method to get a DbxUploader object, use run(DbxStreamWriter) for a callback style or use run(InputStream) to directly copy data from an input stream.
